{"type": "article", "id": 22338, "title": "喜欢牛仔吗？这里有 5 个新品牌你可能想知道", "description": "ACNE、J Brand、R 13 越来越红，你可以看看这些还很小众的品牌。", "date": "2016-02-17T07:00:45Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 3126, "name": "牛仔"}, {"id": 23459, "name": "Bliss and Mischief"}, {"id": 23460, "name": "Rachel Comey"}, {"id": 23461, "name": "Kéji"}, {"id": 23462, "name": "Tortoise Jeans"}, {"id": 23463, "name": "Wåven"}], "category": 19, "author": 399912, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 177, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607101334GjHgqQDfx4bKMeaS.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">牛仔大概算是能在春夏秋冬都能穿得潇洒的面料。即便你不是牛仔的粉丝，衣柜中不知不觉也会有几条牛仔裤，这真的是一种随便穿也不会错得太离谱的品类。</p>\n<p class=\"\">春天来了，可能你又想屯点新货，给你推荐几个新的品牌。</p>\n<h2>1.Bliss and Mischief</h2>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101323OFtKasYdjAL2hN54.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071013241b690E8zAJRHcvgf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101324Rt4Z8HCLuF0mwiQN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101325YZtWadUxuVXjGPwf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.508\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">如果你喜欢花哨的牛仔裤，比如牛仔裤上绣一朵两朵花，Bliss and Mischief 也许是个不错的选择。这个品牌由设计师Hillary Justin 在 2014 年创立，说是设计灵感同时来自于自家后院的仙人掌和加州国家公园里的树。风格是牛仔裤上有刺绣，最近还推出了一个向 1982 年美国复古牛仔致敬的系列。此外，除了牛仔，也做一些上衣方巾，还有童装。牛仔裤的价格在 300 — 400 美元不等。</p>\n<h2>2.Rachel Comey</h2>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101325y29FPg0OnS7NCd3J.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66779089\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101326NUEzZv8L0X53OGpS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.10474308\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101326BmaHwigCZGuXdt87.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.96114865\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071013262NpqdyLQMIZBG3kD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.09765625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071013270CDQRhtEbr9SU4po.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.95117845\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">Rachel Comey 并不是一个只做牛仔的品牌，还做其他面料的连衣裙、衬衣和裤装。不过磨损牛仔面料是这个品牌的一个亮点。设计师 Rachel Comey 最开始设计的是男装，到 2004 年才开始涉足女装。所以，这不是一个崭新的品牌，不过有可能你不知道它的牛仔设计。牛仔裤的价格大约在 350 美元左右。</p>\n<h2>3.Kéji</h2>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101327RcLG49dJ6U7FBaO2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.95294118\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101328SAodT8a9UY0hwXKz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.9544688\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016060710132848QyTC6sUoFG5Jqh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.94957983\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101329r74E9cT5bz1iP3DS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73575949\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">Kéji 还真算是一个新的牛仔品牌，目前只推出过两季。 Net-a-Porter 的前买手 Katie Green 做了这个自己的牛仔线，以日本艺术为灵感，除了牛仔裤还包括外套短裙等。这位香港长大的设计师还有在英国裁缝街 Savile Row 受训的经历。<br></p>\n<h2>4.Tortoise Jeans</h2>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101329UOZe6VcnWMiFCBI9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.55555556\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101330PO4hC2bdeJsSI1Mg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.55555556\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071013307QFrsWZy8jtPNlMb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.54444444\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071013302v7THaoirc30nSbj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.54444444\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101331fKDSTs0VyHoXP6Mh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.54444444\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">这个洛杉矶的牛仔品牌倡导环保。说是优化了生产牛仔面料的水洗工艺，减少了有害的化学物质使用也使面料更耐磨。Tortoise Jeans 既有男装也有女装，风格也比较简单，也会有拼接的设计。但是价格很贵，在 2000 美元左右。</p>\n<h2>5.Wåven</h2>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101331t3uqIVOJTc4D6sC1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73162393\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101332ZW1VNIbdf0wGeLax.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0754717\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101332jqTSeWQmDVkzbHl0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.1802935\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101332ixTCoybaS97wV4ZW.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.18697479\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101333fFrlmtjLkJgOGI8A.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.17910448\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101333VpCgyJd3hWDoIPL8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.05805243\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">这个伦敦的品牌痴迷于做斯堪的纳维亚风格的牛仔设计。可能是指极简的设计，还有类似“跑马的汉子”那种粗犷感。新的一季牛仔面料采用了白色、浅粉、浅灰、浅蓝的颜色，看起来像是在弱化牛仔的概念，据说是从日本人的工装汲取的设计灵感。价格不算太贵，牛仔裤大约在 50 美元上下。</p>\n<p class=\"\">题图和文内图来自：Bliss and Mischief 官方网站、Rachel Comey @ INS ，Kéji @INS ，Tortoise Jeans 官方网站，Wåven @INS 。</p>\n\n\n"}